ed="T" n="0799c20"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0799c20"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000011010"><placeName>潤州</placeName><placeName>招隱寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A010979">朗然</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0799c21"/><persName key="A010979">釋朗然</persName>，俗姓<name>魏</name>，世襲冠冕，其先隨<placeName key="PL000000000103">東晉</placeName>南<lb
ed="T" n="0799c22"/>渡，則為<placeName key="PL000000011208">南徐</placeName>人也。<date notBefore-iso="+0713-12-26" key="j19818371992113" notAfter-iso="+0742-02-13"><name>開元</name>中</date>入道，受業於<placeName key="PL000000010972"><placeName>丹<lb
ed="T" n="0799c23"/>陽</placeName><placeName>開元寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A010980">齊<roleName>大師</roleName></persName>。<date notBefore-iso="+0742-02-14" key="j19921141993438" notAfter-iso="+0745-09-30"><name>天寶</name>初</date>受具<anchor xml:id="beg0799sgsz22"/>於<anchor xml:id="end0799sgsz22"/><placeName key="PL000000011601"><placeName>杭州</placeName><placeName>華嚴<lb
ed="T" n="0799c24"/>寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A010882">光<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>。後徙<placeName key="PL000000011596">靈隱寺</placeName>，依<persName key="A010981">遠<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>，通《四分<lb
ed="T" n="0799c25"/>律鈔》<ptr target="#n1290"/>，重稟<placeName key="PL000000013239">越州</placeName><persName key="A004177">曇一<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>，精研律部，講訓<lb
ed="T" n="0799c26"/>生徒，四遠響應。<persName key="A004378">肅宗</persName><date from-iso="+0757-01-29" key="j19975771997960" to-iso="+0758-02-16"><name>至德</name>二年</date>，恩命舉移，隷<lb
ed="T" n="0799c27"/>名於<placeName key="PL000000056477">慈和寺</placeName>。<date notBefore-iso="+0760-06-12" key="j19988071999309" notAfter-iso="+0761-10-27"><name>上元</name>中</date>，刺史<persName key="A010982">韋儇</persName>又請為<placeName key="PL000000011010">招隱</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0799c28"/>統領大德。即以其年講授之暇，著《古今決》十<lb
ed="T" n="0799c29"/>卷，解釋《四分律鈔》數十萬言，繁雜義例，條貫<pb ed="T" n="0800a" xml:id="T50.2061.0800a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0800a01"/>甚明，大行於世。觀其先列古人之義，有所<lb
ed="T" n="0800a02"/>不安，則判斷之，故號「決」也。《決》中自序：初依<lb
ed="T" n="0800a03"/><placeName key="PLG00000000023">天竺</placeName><persName key="A013717">威<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>學習，復從<persName key="A010981">遠</persName>、<persName key="A004177">一</persName>二師也。凡戒<lb
ed="T" n="0800a04"/>壇則二十六登。皆為壇席之主。《律鈔》凡二十<lb
ed="T" n="0800a05"/>八過講。有饋遺者隨豐薄，受而轉施悲、信<lb
ed="T" n="0800a06"/>二田<ptr target="#n1255"/>。凡於教理，披文究義，皆言宿習<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1256"/>之力<lb
ed="T" n="0800a07"/>也。執持戒檢，斯須不違。<date from-iso="+0777-11-09" key="j20051662005254" to-iso="+0778-02-05"><name>大曆</name>十二年冬</date>癸<lb
ed="T" n="0800a08"/>卯<ptr target="#n1256"/>，趺坐如常，恬然化滅，時年五十四，僧臘三<lb
ed="T" n="0800a09"/>十五。<date from-iso="+0778-02-06" key="j20052552005343" to-iso="+0778-05-05">越十三年春</date>辛酉，建塔<anchor xml:id="begd1e24980"/>於<anchor xml:id="endd1e24980"/><placeName key="PL000000011007">山</placeName>西原，縗<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1525"/><lb
ed="T" n="0800a10"/>麻之徒泣血千計。高行弟子<persName key="A010984">清浩</persName>、<persName key="A010985">擇言</persName>等。請<lb
ed="T" n="0800a11"/>益弟子御史中丞<placeName key="PL000000018627">洪府</placeName>觀察使<persName key="A010982">韋儇</persName>、吏部員<lb
ed="T" n="0800a12"/>外<persName key="A000519">李華</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000010986">潤州</placeName>刺史<persName key="A010986">韓賁</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000013012">湖州</placeName>刺史<persName key="A010987">韋損</persName>、御史<lb
ed="T" n="0800a13"/>大夫<persName key="A010988">劉暹</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000010986">潤州</placeName>刺史<persName key="A010989">樊<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>冕</sic><corr>晃</corr></choice></persName>，皆歸心奉信。屯田<lb
ed="T" n="0800a14"/>員外郎<persName key="A010990">柳識</persName>為碑頌焉。</p>
